page.title: 10FARMING CARNEVAS MACHINERY
page.content: {TRACTORS}:1 John Deere 2040S,1 David Brown 996,1 International 275,1 Massey Ferguson T20 . {TRAILERS}:1 Warrick tipping,1 Marshall corn ,1 Brown's bale. {TRACTOR ACCESSORIES:}1 Brown's bale- sledge,1 front loader,1 Brown's bale- grab ,1 Pantor harrow,1 Bamford disk harrow,1 Massey drill,2 cultivators,1 rippavator,1 John Deere 4 furrow plough, 1 S.K.H. 1200 weight fertilizer spreader,1 S.K.H. dung-spreader,1 Everis and Wall sprayer ,1 hay turner. {TRANSPORT:}1 Landrover, 1 Karda horse box,and 1 home made transport box. {GRASS-MOWERS}: 1PZ mower,and 1 Major mower,1 Briggs and Stratton 6 HP lawn mower, and 1 Briggs and Stratton 5 HP lawn mower.
